<subSubSection pageId="33" pageNumber="132" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="33.[242,1474,682,741]" pageId="33" pageNumber="132">
ETYMOLOGY. — The senior species taxon probably named after J. F. de Galaup La Pérouse, a French navigator who explored the Pacific ocean and shipwrecked in Vanikoro of the Santa Cruz group, SE 
<collectingCountry box="[1150,1332,717,741]" name="Solomon Islands" pageId="33" pageNumber="132">Solomon Islands</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
